profile_positions.description:
Coolblue is one of the largest online shops in the Netherlands & Belgium (and in 2020 we also started in Germany!), and has only one goal: making customers smile. :) Some smiles come easily, some take a little extra, but at Coolblue it's all in the details. Making customers (ánd candidates) happy is in our DNA. :)

My responsibilities at Coolblue include:
★ Screen and evaluate candidates using appropriate assessment approaches, including resume screening, short listing candidates via phone screenings and face-2-face/digital interviews;
★ Guide candidates through the full recruiting life cycle and make sure they have an amazing candidate journey;
★ Work in a Tech Recruitment Scrum team with sprints of one month (daily stand-up, sprint planning) + acting like a Scrum Master every couple of months;
★ Advise hiring managers on interviewing techniques / mind-set on certain IT profiles;
★ Work with the leadership teams to determine hiring targets and to develop profiles and specifications of IT Professionals;
★ Develop strategic and creative strategies using a combination of direct sourcing, online postings, referrals, networking, headhunting and other relevant methods;
★ Keeping track of recruiting metrics (e.g. time-to-hire and cost-per-hire);
★ Leading & participating in recruitment projects to keep improving Coolblues candidate journey. 
★ Spokesperson for Coolblue’s recruitment Diversity & Inclusion group

★ Participate in job fairs and career events + organizing in-house events to engage candidates;

Specialized in recruiting:
- Scrum Masters
- Product Owners
- Salesforce Developers
- Principal Developers
- Mobile Developers
- Python Developers 
- Application Specialists
- UX/UI Designers
- Team Leads
- Dev Managers
- C# developers
-  IT Security

Responsibilities:
★ acquisition of projects and relationship management;
★ discuss and develop recruitment strategy with customer;
★ independent search, recruitment and selection; 
★ developing and managing customer- and candidate network;
★ editor + online marketing optimalization company LinkedIn + Facebook page
